title: Jabra Mini Bluetooth Headset RealTree Outdoor Edition (U.S. Retail Packaging)
feature: Streams multimedia, power nap feature (battery-saving mode), and spoken battery and connection status
Jabra Assist App Helps Locate the headset if it has been misplaced
Includes softly molded ear gels and/or adjustable ear hook for a custom fit
Up to 9 hours of talk time and 9 days of standby time
description: Crafted for the outdoor lifestyle, the Jabra Mini Outdoor Edition boasts the official Real tree Xtra pattern. The headset has been designed for all-day hands free use and offers two wearing style options - with ear gels or an ear hook. To extend its battery life, Jabra Mini Outdoor Edition has a power nap feature, which allows the headset to turn itself off after having been disconnected from your device for a full hour.
